name: Imaginary Castle
description:
Amusement Park Series - Imaginary Castle [1]

VHS extract processed with Panasonic WJ-AVE7 video mixer. Rescanned from CRT TV.

The Amusement Park Collection was born in a fleamarket where I found a promotional VHS tape of a popular amusement park. From there, I searched for more vintage tapes and started the analog processing. However, a few days later, I felt that it was still a bit shallow so I started on a new research path. I began looking into Reddit themeparks and rollercoasters communities and, as a continuation of that, I joined Discord servers where I met great and passionate rollercoaster enthusiasts that helped me to discover lots of cool rides. It has been a great journey.
